    <item>
      <title>特朗普的加密项目购买与孙宇晨相关的代币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-s-crypto-project-buys-tokens-associated-with-justin-sun</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的加密平台 World Liberty Financial 似乎已经将通过 Coinbase Global Inc. 推出的价值约 1000 万美元的所谓包装比特币 (wrapped Bitcoin) 兑换成了与项目顾问孙宇晨 (Justin Sun) 相关的类似代币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-s-crypto-project-buys-tokens-associated-with-justin-sun</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 18:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
