    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 的 Saylor 想要更多“智能杠杆”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/microstrategy-s-saylor-wants-to-add-more-intelligent-leverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 联合创始人兼董事长迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 表示，一旦当前的筹款计划用尽，这家互联网时代的软件制造商将转向杠杆比特币代理计划，将更多精力放在固定收益证券上，以筹集资金购买加密货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/microstrategy-s-saylor-wants-to-add-more-intelligent-leverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德 ETF 购买首批通过区块链发行的市政债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/blackrock-etf-buys-first-muni-bonds-issued-through-blockchain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 的一只基金购买了今年早些时候发行的市政债券，这是一项首次完全依赖区块链技术的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/blackrock-etf-buys-first-muni-bonds-issued-through-blockchain</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 14:55:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币涨势在首次突破 108,000 美元后暂停</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-btc-rally-pauses-after-scaling-108-000-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们等待美联储预期中的降息，并评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对加密货币的支持所带来的乐观情绪，比特币在首次突破 108,000 美元后稍作喘息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-btc-rally-pauses-after-scaling-108-000-for-the-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
